Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.85,0:00:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop.{fb}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.59,0:00:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's far enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.17,0:00:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lay a hand on Her Highness...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.24,0:00:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Orange.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.72,0:00:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Bat.{/fb}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.24,0:01:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,From Andalusian Leader to all units.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.86,0:01:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Target the enemy transports.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.74,0:01:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Prioritize them, even if Cataphracts intercept us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.51,0:01:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We will use Kaufmann 6 as an anchor to perform wire swingby
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.30,0:01:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and return to Base Trident.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.50,0:01:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Best of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.27,0:01:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.19,0:01:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Target sighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.24,0:01:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All units, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.14,0:01:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind's too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.43,0:01:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Our rounds are drifting!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.29,0:01:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't break formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.30,0:01:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They're in the same boat as us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit them before we're in melee range!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.44,0:01:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's lots of heavy, orbiting debris.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.37,0:01:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't hit them from this distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.07,0:01:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We have plenty of ammunition!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:01:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep firing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.78,0:02:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Andalusian 33, I've taken a hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.08,0:02:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Light damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.21,0:02:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Continuing missi—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Andalusian 33!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Andalusian 22!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.81,0:02:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.61,0:02:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How could anyone land a shot in this wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.69,0:02:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Strong heat signature approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.19,0:02:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.18,0:02:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.70,0:02:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tharsis!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.06,0:02:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.89,0:02:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.12,0:02:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Slaine Troyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Andalusian 11!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.12,0:02:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not hitting him...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.41,0:02:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.02,0:03:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Slaine Troyard, have come,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,bearing the royal protection of my princess Asseylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.68,0:03:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been in love with the Earth ever since I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.81,0:03:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,With her blue ocean. With her blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She is blessed with water, air, and light—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.65,0:03:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,a world rich in living beings and natural resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.12,0:03:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost my life on that world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.91,0:03:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, my eyes were opened to the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.41,0:03:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I now understand how insulting it is for the Terrans to take that planet for granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They carelessly devour her resources, \Ndestroy her nature, and seek only vain pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How foolish they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.09,0:03:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We must free the Earth from her exploiters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.89,0:03:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,As first princess of the Vers empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Asseylum Vers Allusia,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,praise the Orbital Knights that have \Ndevoted themselves to this great cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point in watching that pirate broadcast?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.03,0:04:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I was just curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.64,0:04:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into the princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought she was on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.19,0:04:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She might have lost all hope \Nof a peaceful resolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be natural for her \Nto side with Mars in the chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.70,0:04:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a Martian too, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Inko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Inko?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.69,0:04:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking that this \Nis our last chance to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.42,0:04:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to report to the ship tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.47,0:04:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And the day after is the launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.81,0:05:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure you're not thinking about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's got nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't break time anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.23,0:05:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get no training at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We're expected to be able to launch in two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.60,0:05:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The soldier we're waiting for \Nwill arrive tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.97,0:05:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We're talking about {\i1}him{\i0}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.44,0:05:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't fully understand \Nwhat the brass are thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.08,0:05:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like sending your king into battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.28,0:05:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes sense if that king wins the battle for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So they're telling us to put him to effective use.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.18,0:05:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd see him fight again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You can say that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing short of a miracle he's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,One would never have guessed from your elegant landing that the gravitational field here is unstable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Your skills have increased tenfold,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Slaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Your words honor me, Count Saazbaum.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I was right to have knighted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How was the battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I destroyed four enemy units.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A clear victory, Sir Slaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't call me that, Mister Harklight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to address me with "Sir."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I must decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I am your manservant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.25,0:06:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're my senior, and I'm a Terran.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You are nonetheless a knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, you shouldn't address me with "Mister," Sir Slaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:06:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.49,0:07:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.77,0:07:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You appear quite well,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.62,0:07:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Lemrina.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.60,0:07:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I am weary, Count Saazbaum.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.79,0:07:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How fares the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.51,0:07:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Conquest of North and South America is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.32,0:07:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We're installing a new government.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.22,0:07:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,As for Eurasia and the Far East,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.56,0:07:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,UE counterattacks continue due to the surrender of the Landing Castles there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.48,0:07:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I ever set foot on Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.82,0:07:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We expect the military strength of the UE to be exhausted soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,At that point, Your Highness will become \Nruler of Earth, as per your imperial blood—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.70,0:07:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not speak of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.97,0:07:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.66,0:07:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Lemrina...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I never asked for this blood \Nto flow through my veins.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I hate it utterly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.29,0:08:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The only reason I am allowed to live is because my blood holds power,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.22,0:08:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,for only royalty can stir Aldnoah to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for my careless remark.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the one who extended the hand of friendship toward me, Count Saazbaum.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I may curse my own blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.34,0:08:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but I am grateful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Slaine?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.21,0:08:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Your Highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you teach me of Earth again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.52,0:08:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Gladly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.16,0:08:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we'll be together again for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.46,0:08:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we make it back alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.93,0:08:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.43,0:08:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll beat the Martians \Nand finally restore peace to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't afford to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.25,0:08:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.40,0:09:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're under attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Martian Cataphract!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's on radar, 20 km south-southwest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Approaching at 50 km/h.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All hands to battle stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.67,0:09:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We're leaving the dock.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The anti-gravity device is still undergoing maintenance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.10,0:09:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What on Earth are you wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.76,0:09:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You were issued a uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't look cute enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.32,0:09:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Cu—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you can pilot the ship, \NI have no objections.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.60,0:09:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizusaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.37,0:09:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I need to remind you why men don't like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Launch the Deucalion!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Send out all operational Cataphract squads!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{eyecatch 10:13}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.61,0:10:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we know about this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The Frozen Elysium, Count Yacoym's Cataphract.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.43,0:10:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Its Aldnoah Drive's specialty is... entropy dilution.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.20,0:10:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.77,0:10:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It saps the molecular kinetic energy \Nof all matter within a one-kilometer radius.{what}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.99,0:10:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It surpasses simple environmental manipulation, creating a field of ultra-low temperature.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.12,0:10:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, little Terrans.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.08,0:10:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How will you attempt to defy the power of Aldnoah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.50,0:10:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,At his current rate of speed, he'll reach the dock of the Deucalion in fifteen minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.19,0:10:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta stall him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.21,0:10:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Stall him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.51,0:10:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna smash that \Nmech of his to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.01,0:10:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Harbinger Platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.84,0:10:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Target spotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.45,0:10:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Switching to frozen land mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.24,0:10:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Increase turbine output to maximum.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:10:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Activate de-icers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.11,0:10:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Open fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.49,0:11:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.56,0:11:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The de-icers aren't working?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.08,0:11:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You can move neither finger nor toe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The name Frozen Elysium is not just for flair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.57,0:11:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Voltage down?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the chemical reactions in my batteries cease?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.13,0:11:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,M-My arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.60,0:11:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Harbinger Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.88,0:11:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.71,0:11:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The rounds aren't connecting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.02,0:11:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A shield?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.53,0:11:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We're screwed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.37,0:12:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gotta think of a way to stall it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.80,0:12:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to smashing it to pieces?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.19,0:12:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm downscaling!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Measuring trajectory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Fall back, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The warheads entered a superconductive state and were deflected as per the Meissner Effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what about air burst mode?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.79,0:12:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No explosions?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the batteries freeze and the processors shut off?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But where does the sapped heat go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it concealing the molecular kinetic energy \Nin a dimensional pocket?{what}{lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.54,0:12:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Flight distance for the warheads' electronic timer fuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.60,0:12:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe fifty meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Its field spreads out one kilometer around it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Twenty shots, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Inaho?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to charge the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.37,0:13:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.81,0:13:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have to reach him before that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.22,0:13:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Have at thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.42,0:13:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Grenade launcher, air burst mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.45,0:13:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Cutting safety distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Flight distance, fifty meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.02,0:13:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.48,0:14:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Inaho!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit's damaged more than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm will probably be mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.58,0:14:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Inaho!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.50,0:14:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Inaho?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.62,0:14:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ensign Kaizuka Inaho reporting for duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.66,0:14:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,GHQ has assigned me to your ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, what's with the formal introduction?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.14,0:14:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You never change, do you, Inaho?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.92,0:14:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Same to you, Inko. Glad you're doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.01,0:14:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}have{\i0} changed, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You can actually show concern for other people now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.84,0:14:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a compliment, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.95,0:15:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Inko?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.49,0:15:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Inaho!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.54,0:15:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull the trigger, Slaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.23,0:15:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've finished off the Terran soldier who vexed us at every turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My mind is finally made up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:16:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,For all of my transgressions against you—\Npast, present, and future—I ask your forgiveness,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Count Saazbaum.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.83,0:16:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The castle is swarming with Terran invaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us escape in the Tharsis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.79,0:16:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With{\i0} Princess Asseylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.44,0:16:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life rests in my hands, Count.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you die with your ambitions unrealized?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.55,0:16:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Or live in a world with Princess Asseylum?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.73,0:16:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Please make your decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.92,0:16:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.58,0:16:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.54,0:16:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Inaho!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:16:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Inaho!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.17,0:16:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.98,0:17:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Inaho's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.99,0:17:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Inaho's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.22,0:17:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Yagarai! Please help!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.06,0:17:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Inaho?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Gunshot to the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.72,0:17:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Bullet passed through the temporal region \Nvia the left eye socket.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.20,0:17:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave him three ccs of adrenaline \Nas emergency treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.15,0:17:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.84,0:17:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You can save him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You can save Inaho, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He needs immediate surgical treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.78,0:17:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And a transfusion, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.17,0:17:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got the right tools and facilities in the underground shelter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.45,0:17:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Magbaredge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.05,0:17:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Give the order to launch the Deucalion!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.04,0:17:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The Aldnoah Drive...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's offline.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.60,0:17:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Warrant Officer Kaizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.01,0:17:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Asseylum...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.36,0:17:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.84,0:17:57.97,Wake up; Nao!,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\c&H110913&\b1\fscx42\fscy38\frz330.6\pos(692.857,315.286)\clip(597,254,694,335)}You can do it, Nao!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:17:58.09,Wake up; Nao!,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\c&H110913&\b1\fscx42\fscy38\frz333.2\pos(673.857,306.286)\clip(587,242,696,348)}You can do it, Nao!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:17:59.09,Wake up; Nao!,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\c&H110913&\b1\frz334.6\fscx42\fscy38\pos(653.857,295.286)\clip(560,225,695,332)}You can do it, Nao!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.16,0:18:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.22,0:18:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Nao's blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.12,0:18:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood spatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But whose?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.10,0:18:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The light of Aldnoah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The activation factor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.34,0:19:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Nao!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.85,0:19:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Deucalion, launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.29,0:19:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,All ahead, dead slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All ahead, dead slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.34,0:19:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We've left the atmosphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.64,0:19:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now coasting on inertia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.70,0:20:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Setting course for Trident Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.04,0:20:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Activate electromagnetic grid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Monitor on all wavelengths.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.32,0:20:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We reached out to the Terrans, \Nand they foolishly batted our hand away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.01,0:20:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Now they sit, sharpening their blades \Nand plotting to steal our lands from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.06,0:20:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It is out of mercy that the \NVers Empire will defeat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.33,0:20:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our enemy. You okay with this, Inaho?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.79,0:20:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We shall take the blue Earth \Nin the name of Vers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.44,0:20:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The world with so much air and water that they refract light, turning the skies and oceans blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.68,0:20:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.57,0:20:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.40,0:20:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let us liberate it from these barbarians.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The sky looks blue because of Rayleigh scattering.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you fetch me some water, Eddelrittuo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Of course! Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.73,0:20:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How was that, Count Saazbaum?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.61,0:20:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.40,0:20:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the spitting image of Princess Asseylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.19,0:20:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,None would ever call your identity into question.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the problem with you men.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:21:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,At no point did I ask how well I'd concealed my identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Masterfully done, Princess Lemrina.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Your majestic speech is sure to have moved the Orbital Knights as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.76,0:21:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Sir Slaine Troyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.94,0:21:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Your consideration means far more to me than compliments on my performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You are too kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.45,0:21:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is nothing else, Sir Slaine, \NI will take my leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.84,0:21:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mister Harklight.{i sure hope he doesn't keep doing this for the entire show}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.32,0:21:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I have returned to your side, my Princess Asseylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.72,0:22:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I am glad to see you in good spirits today.{das creepy}{lmao}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.05,0:23:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord0\pos(0,0)\p1\c&H000000&\blur2}m -15 660 l 1300 660 l 1300 740 l -15 740
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.44,0:22:29.49,ED-ep13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}Come on, tell me why we are here
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.49,0:22:32.50,ED-ep13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}This endless, thriving world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.50,0:22:34.07,ED-ep13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}When I cry in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.07,0:22:37.69,ED-ep13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}But you've got the lonely voice
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.60,0:22:41.67,ED-ep13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}Just stop what you're doing for me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:43.73,ED-ep13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}It's not very good for you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.73,0:22:46.39,ED-ep13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}We should know where we're going
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.39,0:22:48.67,ED-ep13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}Nobody knows
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.67,0:22:51.32,ED-ep13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}Fly high
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.32,0:22:55.16,ED-ep13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}How you've outlasted me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.16,0:23:00.53,ED-ep13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}Bullets fall like rain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.93,0:23:04.99,ED-ep13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}And chase us like shooting stars
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.99,0:23:07.65,ED-ep13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}You're carrying something in your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.65,0:23:12.95,ED-ep13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}Everything you see around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.95,0:23:18.11,ED-ep13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}Break your doubt to get out the other side
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.11,0:23:19.82,ED-ep13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}So face reality
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.82,0:23:24.73,ED-ep13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}You can be who has the only one
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.73,0:23:28.15,ED-ep13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}It will always be so good
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.15,0:23:31.95,ED-ep13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}It's so good for me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.95,0:23:34.77,ED-ep13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}Everyone around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.77,0:23:38.50,ED-ep13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}So take my hand
